data.description: Beautiful Spacious home in the well established Brook Hollow Subdivision located in South Abilene. This move in ready home boast 3 spacious bedrooms with plantation shutters, walk-in closets and more. Plenty of storage throughout. Spacious open living and dining, perfect for entertaining family and friends. Attached Bonus room with hot tub, half bath and more. Spacious kitchen with plenty of cabinets and counter space. Great floor plan. Updated Master and Guest baths. Great backyard with garden and more. Class 4 Roof. Come and see. Bonus room not included in Taylor Cad square feet.Please verify measurements.
data.whatILove: Spacious with large bedrooms. Versatile great room( living, den, dining). Bonus rec room with earth type wood burning heat stove not figured in total sq. footage,add 500 sq. Ft. to base building for this feature. Electric updated in 2005 and 2013.
